      WeatherStation getWeatherStation(String wsType, String loc)
      Create a WeatherStation of type wsType, location loc

        public WeatherStation getWeatherStation(String wsType,
                                        String loc)
        Create a WeatherStation of type wsType, location loc
        Note: For CSV or ACU, the location is the location of the file containing the values; for API and XML it is the appropriate identifier for the NOAA API and XML requests.
        Parameters:
        wsType - weather station type (API, XML, ACU, CSV)
        loc - "location" usage dependent on WeatherStation type.
        Returns:
        WeatherStation object
